Class GodfatherUpdateServlet

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig
    @WebServlet("/adminGodfatherUpdate")
public class GodfatherUpdateServlet
extends FilterServlet
    This Servlet is used by the Admin to update a Godfathers personal data (except password) or to remove the Godfather
    Allowed http methods: POST, DELETE
    Author:
    MichelBlank
